price: 43. Mokano ya umma(1) nyoso mokoki koleka eleko na yango te, mpe ekokutuama te.
arabic: مَا تَسۡبِقُ مِنۡ أُمَّةٍ أَجَلَهَا وَمَا يَسۡتَـٔۡخِرُونَ
footnotes: 1 Umma: Awa elakisi: Etonga, bótala lisusu na suratu Al-Baqarah na mokapo: 128.

version.title: Lingala translation
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Lingala language, translated by Zakaria Muhammad Balngogo.
